    "abstract": "The present study underscores both the potential and limitations of LLMs in automating scoping reviews. Automating the entire scoping review without human intervention is sub-optimal. Using a more controlled approach balances the strengths of LLMs with the need for human judgment, supporting not only the replication of scientific reviews but also their continuous refinement and follow-up over time.",
